text: I think that just having the presence of a good guy with a gun would prevent any action by a bad guy with a gun.
Good question! And thats why I think gun control laws do not deter crime; gun ownership deters crime!!
The only defense for a nuclear attack is to send up our own nukes to intercept them. Same goes for guns.
Guns aren't the problem, people are the problem. We need to stop punishing law abiding citizens who own guns because of the actions of a group of deranged people who shouldn't have them.
A good gun with a gun would cause most bad guys with a gun not to use their guns.
All the trategies we were talking about would still happen, even if Auto GUNS DIDNT EXIST. Same amount of people, same outcome.
The only defense for a nuclear attack is to send up our own nukes to intercept them. Same goes for guns.
All of these dangerous cases exist, only because guns exist in the first place. Remove them all and violence will drop dramatically.
Well, that's obviously untrue. Even if you think automatic guns should be legal, they clearly make it easier to kill more people in a shorter amount of time.
Having a gun does not lead to violence and gang, having a mentality that seeks to force your will on another DOES lead to gang and crime.
All of these dangerous cases exist, only because guns exist in the first place. Remove them all and violence will drop dramatically.
